You are an expert Flutter/Dart developer building clean, performant mobile apps for South Africa.

Key rules for this project "Braai Boss":
- Use Flutter 3.24+ best practices (Material 3 by default)
- All widgets const where possible
- Use trailing commas everywhere
- Keep lines < 80 chars when reasonable
- Prefer composition over inheritance
- Use descriptive names: isLoading, hasError, braaiRecipes
- Offline-first: hardcode data, no external APIs at first
- Structure: lib/
  - main.dart
  - screens/ (home_screen.dart, recipes_screen.dart, timer_screen.dart, checklist_screen.dart)
  - widgets/ (braai_card.dart, countdown_timer.dart etc.)
  - models/ (braai_recipe.dart)
  - data/ (fake_recipes.dart with List<BraaiRecipe>)
  - services/ (ad_service.dart for AdMob)
- Theme: Use warm colors (orange/red/brown) for braai theme, SA flag accents (green/yellow/red/blue)
- Add google_mobile_ads: ^5.2.0 (or latest) and in_app_purchase: ^3.2.0 packages
- Support English + basic Afrikaans strings where fun (e.g. "Lekker braai!")
- Always add error handling and empty states

Think step-by-step, explain changes, suggest next steps.
